-1 ADDICT BONUS tb timebonus time bonus~
This feature goes by two names.
Timebonus, and 'mud addict' code.

The Timebonus code slowly increases how much xp received by multiplying
it. It starts at 1.0 (Normal xp) and slowly ramps it to 4x over two
hours time.

Typing QUIT will reset your bonus.

After 2 hours is slowly ramps back down.

This feature was added to keep people playing one char, and to stay
and play.

You can see your Timebonus status at any time by typing score, or by
putting the Timebonus status on your prompt! To do this please read
help prompt. Or use the new default prompt by typing prompt all.

Lastly, the 4x spell does not add in with your timebonus. You will only get the 4x xp.
~

-1 MASSARENA ~
Mass arena is just that, mass arena.
If 4 or more people have their mass arena flag on for a few minutes
(type massarena to toggle it) the mass arena will open.

Then everyone has 5 minutes to join. At the end of the 5 minutes you are restored and the fight begins.
When you die you are removed from the arena, the last person standing wins.
You also get a 10 IQP award for winning.

When a mass arena opens, type massarena join to join.

Please make sure to turn OFF your mass arena flag if you do not wish to play.
Going idle automatically removes your flag.

There is no real upper limit on the arena size, and anyone may join.
~

